<i>adverb</i>: 힐끗 [힐끋], 한때 [한때], 일시 [일씨], 얼씬얼씬 [얼씬얼씬], 얼씬 [얼씬], 설핏 [설핏], 간략히 [갈랴키], 간단히 [간단히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>힐끗 [힐끋]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with one glance; with one look</dd><br>
<dd>슬쩍 한 번 흘겨보는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of looking at something briefly one time.</dd><br>
<dd>2. briefly; quickly</dd><br>
<dd>눈에 잠깐 띄는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of coming in and out of view briefly.</dd><br>
<dt>한때 [한때]</dt><br>
<dd>temporarily; briefly; at one time</dd><br>
<dd>어느 시기의 짧은 동안에.</dd><br>
<dd>For a certain short period of time.</dd><br>
<dt>일시 [일씨]</dt><br>
<dd>temporarily; briefly; transiently</dd><br>
<dd>어느 시기의 짧은 동안에.</dd><br>
<dd>For a certain short period of time.</dd><br>
<dt>얼씬얼씬 [얼씬얼씬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. briefly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 장소나 눈앞에 잠깐씩 나타났다 없어졌다 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of appearing for a moment and disappearing in front of a place or one's eyes again and again.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flatteringly</dd><br>
<dd>교묘한 말과 행동으로 계속해서 남의 비위를 맞추는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of trying to please another person with sly words and behavior again and again.</dd><br>
<dt>얼씬 [얼씬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. briefly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 장소나 눈앞에 잠깐 나타났다 없어지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of appearing for a moment and disappearing in front of a place or one's eyes.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flatteringly</dd><br>
<dd>교묘한 말과 행동으로 남의 비위를 맞추는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of trying to please another person with sly words and behavior.</dd><br>
<dt>설핏 [설핏]</dt><br>
<dd>1. dimly</dd><br>
<dd>해의 밝은 빛이 약해진 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the brightness of the sunlight becomes weaker.</dd><br>
<dd>2. briefly</dd><br>
<dd>잠깐 나타나거나 떠오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of appearing or coming to one's mind for a brief moment.</dd><br>
<dd>3. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>얕은 잠에 빠져든 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of falling into a light sleep.</dd><br>
<dt>간략히 [갈랴키]</dt><br>
<dd>briefly; concisely</dd><br>
<dd>간단하고 짤막하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Simply and briefly.</dd><br>
<dt>간단히 [간단히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. briefly</dd><br>
<dd>길거나 복잡하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that does not make something lengthy or complicated.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lighlty; little</dd><br>
<dd>번거롭거나 많지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that does not cause much trouble or require too many things.</dd><br>
<dd>3. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>다루거나 하기가 꽤 쉽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that makes something easy to handle or do.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>